property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
select 
'RFXItemValue_' || COALESCE("RFXItemValue"."ItemId" ||  "RFXItemValue"."SliceId" ||  "RFXItemValue"."VersionId") as "ID",
'RFXItem_' || COALESCE("RFXItemValue"."ItemId" ||  '_' ||  "RFXItemValue"."VersionId") as "RFXDocumentItem",
"RFXItemValue"."ExpiryDate" AS "ExpiryDate",
"RFXItemValue"."QUANTITY" AS "Quantity",
CAST("RFXItemValue"."TimeCreated" AS TIMESTAMP) AS "TimeCreated",
"RFXItemValue"."TiedRank" AS "TiedRank",
"RFXItemValue"."EXTENDEDPRICE" AS "ExtendedPrice",
--"RFXItemValue"."BESTPRICE" AS "BestPrice", 
"RFXItemValue"."STATUS" AS "Status",
"RFXItemValue"."PRICE" AS "Price",
"RFXItemValue"."Active" AS "Active",
"RFXItemValue"."REUSEQUOTE" AS "Reusequote",
"RFXItemValue"."NextVersion" AS "NextVersion",
"RFXItemValue"."SliceId" AS "SliceId",
CAST("RFXItemValue"."Rank" AS INT) AS "Rank",
"RFXItemValue"."TimeUpdated" AS "TimeUpdated",
CAST("RFXItemValue"."AODDataSyncScn" AS INT) AS "AodDataSyncScn",
"RFXItemValue"."SAVINGS" AS "Savings",
"RFXItemValue"."EffectiveDate" AS "EffectiveDate",
--"RFXItemValue"."ExpiryDate" AS "QuantityAmount",
CAST("RFXItemValue"."EXTENDEDPRICE_AmountInReportingCurrency" AS FLOAT) AS "ExtendedPriceAmountInReportingCurrency",
CAST("RFXItemValue"."EXTENDEDPRICE_ApproxAmountInBaseCurrency" AS FLOAT) AS "ExtendedPriceApproxAmountInBaseCurrency",
CAST("RFXItemValue"."EXTENDEDPRICE_Amount"  AS FLOAT) AS "ExtendedPriceAmount",
"RFXItemValue"."EXTENDEDPRICE_ConversionDate" AS "ExtendedPriceConversionDate",
"RFXItemValue"."EXTENDEDPRICE_Currency_UniqueName" AS "ExtendedPriceCurrencyUniqueName",
CAST("RFXItemValue"."PRICE_AmountInReportingCurrency" AS FLOAT) AS "PriceAmountInReportingCurrency",
CAST("RFXItemValue"."PRICE_ApproxAmountInBaseCurrency" AS FLOAT) AS "PriceApproxAmountInBaseCurrency",
CAST("RFXItemValue"."PRICE_Amount" AS FLOAT) AS "PriceAmount",
"RFXItemValue"."PRICE_ConversionDate" AS "PriceConversionDate",
"RFXItemValue"."PRICE_Currency_UniqueName" AS "PriceCurrencyUniqueName",
CAST("RFXItemValue"."SAVINGS_Amount1_AmountInReportingCurrency" AS FLOAT) AS "SavingsAmount1AmountInReportingCurrency",
CAST("RFXItemValue"."SAVINGS_Amount1_ApproxAmountInBaseCurrency" AS FLOAT) AS "SavingsAmount1ApproxAmountInBaseCurrency",
CAST("RFXItemValue"."SAVINGS_Amount1_Amount" AS FLOAT) AS "SavingsAmount1Amount",
"RFXItemValue"."SAVINGS_Amount1_ConversionDate" AS "SavingsAmount1ConversionDate",
"RFXItemValue"."SAVINGS_Amount1_Currency_UniqueName" AS "SavingsAmount1CurrencyUniqueName",
CAST("RFXItemValue"."SAVINGS_Amount2_AmountInReportingCurrency" AS FLOAT) AS "SavingsAmount2AmountInReportingCurrency",
CAST("RFXItemValue"."SAVINGS_Amount2_Amount" AS FLOAT) AS "SavingsAmount2Amount",
"RFXItemValue"."SAVINGS_Amount2_ConversionDate" AS "SavingsAmount2ConversionDate",
"RFXItemValue"."SAVINGS_Amount2_Currency_UniqueName" AS "SavingsAmount2CurrencyUniqueName",
CAST("RFXItemValue"."NextVersion_VersionId" AS INT) AS "NextVersionVersionId"
--,"RFXItemValue"."" AS "RfxDocumentItem"
FROM "RFXItemValue"
